Titolo: Angry Birds Evolution

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Angry Birds Evolution, later renamed to Angry Birds Evolution 2020, is a free-to-play 3-D turn-based role-playing puzzle game that was released worldwide by Rovio Entertainment on June 15, 2017. The game plays similar to Angry Birds Epic, also developed by Chimera Entertainment, with the exception that a player is slinging birds toward the enemies to defeat them instead of using weapons.
The game has received the Editor's Choice award on the Google Play Store. According to mobile research firm Sensor Tower, it has grossed more than $30 million worldwide, as of July 2018.

Genere: Puzzle 

Valutazione: N/A
